ing="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rod-stewart">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart)</a>因感染链球菌性喉炎被迫取消了他在拉斯维加斯举行的第 200 场演出。</p><p>斯图尔特在 Instagram 上发帖称，由于细菌感染导致身体不适，他“对错过这场第 200 场演出庆祝活动感到非常遗憾”。这位 79 岁的音乐家将于周三（8 月 7 日）在凯撒宫罗马斗兽场结束他的“The Hits”演出。</p><p>他补充道：“大多数人都能患上链球菌性喉炎，但显然我不行。我彻底崩溃了。我期待这场音乐会很久了。对于由此造成的任何不便，我深表歉意。”</p><p>然而，斯图尔特确实宣布他将于 2025 年开始在拉斯维加斯驻地。</p><p> Instagram 上的一篇帖子写道：“维加斯，我玩得太开心了，所以我们要回来再演一次！不要错过拉斯维加斯驻地安可秀。”</p><p>该演出将于 2025 年 3 月 12 日至 22 日和 5 月 29 日至 6 月 8 日在凯撒宫斗兽场举行，门票将于太平洋时间周一上午 10 点（英国夏令时下午 6 点）开始销售，您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/rod-stewart-tickets/artist/736200 https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Frod-stewart-tickets%2Fartist%2F736200" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-Yd5cMJzhm/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:6